2026-04-02 16:48:20.222 | INFO     | __main__:demo_dataworks_tools:108 - 💡 演示4: 如何调用DataWorks工具的示例代码
2026-04-02 16:48:20.222 | INFO     | __main__:demo_dataworks_tools:109 - ================================================================================
2026-04-02 16:48:20.222 | INFO     | __main__:demo_dataworks_tools:138 - 

# Python代码示例
from app.mcp.manager import MCPManager

manager = MCPManager()
await manager.initialize()

# 示例1: 列出所有项目
projects = await manager.call_tool("dataworks", "ListProjects", {})

# 示例2: 列出指定项目的表
tables = await manager.call_tool("dataworks", "ListTables", {
    "projectName": "your_project_name"
})

# 示例3: 获取表详情
table_info = await manager.call_tool("dataworks", "GetTable", {
    "projectName": "your_project_name",
    "tableName": "your_table_name"
})

# 示例4: 列出任务实例
tasks = await manager.call_tool("dataworks", "ListTaskInstances", {
    "projectName": "your_project_name"
})
        
